message.content:
I need to identify the tax accrued but not yet paid from the balance sheet. This would be listed as "Taxes Payable" in the liabilities section.

Looking at the balance sheet, I can see the "Taxes Payable" line item:

| Account | Initial_amount | Initial_date | End_amount | End_date |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Taxes Payable | 0.00 | 2023-12-31 | 1428630.43 | 2024-02-05 |

This shows that:
- The initial value of taxes payable as of 2023-12-31 was 0.00
- The end value of taxes payable as of 2024-02-05 was 1428630.43

These represent the tax accrued but not yet paid at the beginning and end of the reporting period.

```json
{"solution": {'initial value': '0.00', 'end value': '1428630.43'}}
```
